{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"0FaG1aU68OaRkl5IK6xhh","title":"Graph Traversal","desc":"","updated":1643451522115,"created":1641835100590,"custom":{},"fname":"science.CS.algos.Graph Traversal","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"4821e7b4509038a2f186e1154b40d408","links":[{"from":{"fname":"science.math.Optimization","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1,"offset":391},"end":{"line":15,"column":37,"offset":427},"indent":[]},"value":"science.CS.algos.Graph Traversal","alias":"science.CS.algos.Graph Traversal"},{"from":{"fname":"science.engineering.technologies.graphs","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1,"offset":428},"end":{"line":24,"column":37,"offset":464},"indent":[]},"value":"science.CS.algos.Graph Traversal","alias":"science.CS.algos.Graph Traversal"}],"anchors":{"":{"type":"header","text":"","value":"","line":9,"column":0,"depth":1},"basic-tree-traversals":{"type":"header","text":"Basic Tree Traversals","value":"basic-tree-traversals","line":12,"column":0,"depth":1},"dfs":{"type":"header","text":"DFS","value":"dfs","line":13,"column":0,"depth":2},"pre-order":{"type":"header","text":"Pre-order","value":"pre-order","line":21,"column":0,"depth":3},"in-order":{"type":"header","text":"In-order","value":"in-order","line":23,"column":0,"depth":3},"post-order-":{"type":"header","text":"Post-order :","value":"post-order-","line":25,"column":0,"depth":3},"bfs":{"type":"header","text":"BFS","value":"bfs","line":28,"column":0,"depth":2},"iteratively-deepening-bfs":{"type":"header","text":"Iteratively deepening BFS","value":"iteratively-deepening-bfs","line":29,"column":0,"depth":3},"heuristic-search":{"type":"header","text":"Heuristic Search","value":"heuristic-search","line":32,"column":0,"depth":2},"a":{"type":"header","text":"A*","value":"a","line":33,"column":0,"depth":3},"dfs-notes":{"type":"header","text":"DFS Notes","value":"dfs-notes","line":37,"column":0,"depth":1},"previsit-and-connected-components":{"type":"header","text":"Previsit and connected components","value":"previsit-and-connected-components","line":58,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":[],"parent":"R3N3tS0RNCjMvqnqSnGZI","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"graph-traversal\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#graph-traversal\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Graph Traversal</h1>\n<h1 id=\"\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"basic-tree-traversals\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#basic-tree-traversals\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Basic Tree Traversals</h1>\n<h2 id=\"dfs\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#dfs\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>DFS</h2>\n<p>T-top(or root)\nL=left\nR=right</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/tree-traversals-inorder-preorder-and-postorder/\">Tree traversals</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"pre-order\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#pre-order\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Pre-order</h3>\n<p>T, L , R </p>\n<h3 id=\"in-order\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#in-order\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>In-order</h3>\n<p>L, T, R</p>\n<h3 id=\"post-order-\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#post-order-\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Post-order :</h3>\n<p>L R T</p>\n<h2 id=\"bfs\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#bfs\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>BFS</h2>\n<h3 id=\"iteratively-deepening-bfs\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#iteratively-deepening-bfs\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Iteratively deepening BFS</h3>\n<h2 id=\"heuristic-search\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#heuristic-search\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Heuristic Search</h2>\n<h3 id=\"a\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#a\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>A*</h3>\n<p> consisten heuristic</p>\n<h1 id=\"dfs-notes\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#dfs-notes\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>DFS Notes</h1>\n<p>Exploring w/ dfs</p>\n<pre class=\"language-{python}\"><code class=\"language-{python}\">\nseen = set()\ndef explore(V:List[Int],E:Dict[Int,Set[int]],v):\n    if v in seen:  #optionally!!!\n        return\n    seen.add(v)\n    previsit(v) # optionally! use if need to detect cycles, other stuff \n    for w in E[v]:\n        explore(V,E,w)\n    postvisit(v) # optionally! useful to keep track of cycles and other stuff\n\n</code></pre>\n<p>Intuition:\nExplore labyrinth: need some <strong>rope</strong> (stack) and <strong>piece of chalk</strong>(visited set). Go along the <strong>rightmost path without chalk marks</strong> (dfs ordering), and return when\nyou reach a dead end.</p>\n<h3 id=\"previsit-and-connected-components\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#previsit-and-connected-components\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Previsit and connected components</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-{python}\"><code class=\"language-{python}\">#...\ncc=dict()\ndef previsit(v,cc):\n   ccnum[v] = cc\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/PublicPersonalKnowledgeBase/notes/4FIxH4rGwMUvVyCogNmHe\">Optimization</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/PublicPersonalKnowledgeBase/notes/iiXbMCqdkdfEMqpCPWrpY\">Graphs</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"wn8PE1RhG0znK1alrGFYv","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1647507231129,"created":1631901573363,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"db285659ccac8b133c384de1ef51de66","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-stefans-notes":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to Stefan's Notes!","value":"welcome-to-stefans-notes","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["mxzxxu8z4e6krz99ht96y9d","W1EOZ27Tqx6RbiA2aW3DI","DyoLE2kwm9rRfRZhBGxPW","idhfogizmtcmvaamtalp3o3","4w8wBCSRvYUnGIZeozW03","vB321AipYCs6ldVC0APs9","h6WVdl1UTWVXeWuMJSZ1f","bth6m0exy9q9loxib1mc4al","4abAmH56ausbldEJbZokx","JyOFJ5NTPSVWMfiDy951X","0OO7fjCpcaGZg5qDRZr8z","138666663","pohXgII67dAxnoufG7yAP","42r6290iqzLPmg9BY7fIp","3hoLerNJHjNkDziIKlFF2","T6meT3UNw0nRorEbzoPSl","hIOTXIIBj3vmhG1xc91lA","tnFlQuOAGPkbU2fZI7Cb1","Jb3w3f4x8kixLhrjUW6S1","LV6q5jlD2xtCF6yYFEqFC","ENDcCZFjAW9h66eDoFg7I","b5IeREnsTbeggC7rmWV0p","nbBlQzRv6upNd7EAsifqo","xcJ4vbwPtrOHtYsSgUaQi","D41QyIueG2TcjTWPyDwAs","3Gihb6jm1N7h9TvHP0b3m","d9qyiiGgDJAIdYBgV8NHB","OA3izVK70lO3wm3AQ9ac0","srwEq3ZSQj5S0POsjEszf","h1ME0EUHZQrdOQWdI83oP"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to Stefan's Notes!\n\n        \n\nLast updated: 2021.12.30\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":4,"useFMTitle":true,"useNoteTitleForLink":true,"mermaid":true,"useKatex":true,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"site":{"copyAssets":true,"siteHierarchies":["root"],"siteRootDir":"docs","siteUrl":"https://petrovs12.github.io","assetsPrefix":"/PublicPersonalKnowledgeBase","usePrettyRefs":true,"title":"Dendron","description":"Personal knowledge space","siteLastModified":true,"gh_edit_branch":"main","duplicateNoteBehavi